          Our network of {trade.name.toLowerCase()} experts covers the entire UK. Find verified professionals in your local area.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4">
        {popularCities.map((city) => (
