        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-amber-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
            1
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Post Your {trade.name} Job</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Describe your {trade.name.toLowerCase()} project requirements in detail. Free to post, no obligations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-amber-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
            2
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Receive {trade.name} Quotes</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Get multiple quotes from verified {trade.name.toLowerCase()} professionals in your area within hours.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-amber-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
            3
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Choose Your Professional</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Compare quotes, check reviews, and hire the right {trade.name.toLowerCase()} professional for your project.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-amber-600 text-white py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
        Ready to Start Your {trade.name} Project?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-amber-100">
        Join thousands of UK homeowners who trust FindTrades to connect with professional {trade.name.toLowerCase()} experts.
      </p>
      <a
        href={`${APP_URL}/request-quote?tradeId=${trade.id}`}
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-white text-amber-600 font-bold text-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
        </svg>
        Get {trade.name} Quotes Now
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
